p = Graph()
g = p - p
assert g.triples == []
assert g.top is None
assert g is not p
q = Graph([('a', ':instance', 'alpha')])
g = q - p
assert g.triples == [('a', ':instance', 'alpha')]
assert g.top == 'a'
assert g is not q is not p
g = p - q
assert g.triples == []
assert g.top is None
g = q - q
assert g.triples == []
assert g.top is None
